        <exercise xml:id="auto_23r8oyyj">
            <statement>
                <p xml:id="auto_6wqk0d06"> Study the following description of a runner’s motion and sketch the corresponding displacement-time graph
                    <ul xml:id="auto_8t0aiz2g">
                        <li xml:id="auto_86mp4ede">
                            <p xml:id="auto_qv5c69gk">
                                The runner starts from rest and accelerates uniformly for <m>\text{ 5 seconds}</m>, covering a displacement of <m>\text{25 meters}</m>.
                            </p>
                        </li>
                        <li xml:id="auto_5iu6ajyc">
                            <p xml:id="auto_3ychqqlh">
                                The runner maintains a constant speed for the next <m>\text{ 10 seconds}</m>, covering an additional <m>\text{ 50 metres}</m>.
                            </p>
                        </li>
                        <li xml:id="auto_yhbpr0oo">
