                <p xml:id="auto_hlvdgsg6">
                <ol xml:id="auto_oyh7gfr0">
                    <li xml:id="auto_vqu7cn4q">
                        <p xml:id="auto_tpamgdgn">
                            The velocity during the first <m>4</m> seconds is <m>\frac{4 \, \text{m}}{4 \, \text{s}} = 1 \, \text{m/s}</m>.
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li xml:id="auto_x8f5b27f">
